OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,FCameras that can detect seatbelt and
OL,7,Fmobile phone offences are being rolled
OL,8,Fout in Devon and Cornwall.
OL,10,FThe camera system is now operational
OL,11,Facross the region, with specific
OL,12,Flocations changing regularly during
OL,13,Fthe course of the 12-month project.
OL,15,FIt is the first long-term use of this
OL,16,Fstate-of-the-art equipment outside
OL,17,FAustralia, and is being used to
OL,18,Fmonitor locations within Devon and
OL,19,FCornwall's 13,500-mile road network.
