OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,FThe cameras take high-speed front-
OL,7,Ffacing and overhead images of vehicles
OL,8,Fand use AI to detect any potential
OL,9,Foffences.
OL,11,FThe images are then verified in the UK
OL,12,Fby a human to determine whether an
OL,13,Foffence has taken place.
OL,15,FIf an offence has been correctly
OL,16,Fidentified, the driver will either be
OL,17,Fsent a warning letter or a notice of
OL,18,Fintended prosecution, depending on the
OL,19,Fseverity.
