OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police, who are
OL,7,Foverseeing the project, have
OL,8,Fpreviously trialled the technology.
OL,9,FEarlier this year, during a two-week
OL,10,Fdeployment in February and March, the
OL,11,Fsystem detected 408 seatbelt and 162
OL,12,Fmobile phone offences.
OL,14,FAdrian Leisk, Head of Road Safety for
OL,15,FDevon and Cornwall Police, said: "The
OL,16,Fvast majority of drivers in Devon and
OL,17,FCornwall are safe, respectful and
OL,18,Fconscientious motorists ` but we know
OL,19,Fmobile phone distraction and not
OL,20,Fwearing a seatbelt are a serious
OL,21,Fdanger to all road users.
OL,26,@wD@bOU
