OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,F"Around a third of all fatal
OL,7,Fcollisions nationally involve someone
OL,8,Fwho wasn't wearing a seatbelt ` and
OL,9,Fnot wearing one means you are twice as
OL,10,Flikely to die in the event of a
OL,11,Fserious collision.
OL,13,F"With regards to those who use mobile
OL,14,Fphones while behind the wheel, we hope
OL,15,Fthese cameras will send a clear
OL,16,Fmessage ` you will get caught.
OL,18,F"You could end up with a hefty fine
OL,19,Fand six penalty points ` which could
OL,20,Fbe enough to cost some drivers their
OL,21,Flicense and livelihood.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
