OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,F"It's just not worth it. Before you
OL,7,Fstart your journey, put your phone
OL,8,Faway in the glovebox or somewhere you
OL,9,Fcannot reach it so the temptation is
OL,10,Fnot there. If it's an emergency, make
OL,11,Fsure you pull in and stop the car
OL,12,Fbefore making that call."
OL,14,FAlison Hernandez, Police and Crime
OL,15,FCommissioner for Devon, Cornwall and
OL,16,Fthe Isles of Scilly, is also chairman
OL,17,Fof the Vision Zero South West road
OL,18,Fsafety partnership.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]
