OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,FCommissioner Hernandez said: "You are
OL,7,Ffour times more likely to crash when
OL,8,Fusing a phone whilst driving, which is
OL,9,Fwhy it is illegal.
OL,11,F"By embracing new technology such as
OL,12,Fthe Acusensus system, we have the
OL,13,Fopportunity to improve driver
OL,14,Fbehaviour and consequently make our
OL,15,Froads safer for everyone."
