OL,3,CAI traffic cameras that detect mobile
OL,4,Cphone use rolled out
OL,6,FDr Jamie Uff, Technical Director with
OL,7,FAECOM who helped to deliver the
OL,8,FAcusensus system, said: "Despite the
OL,9,Foften-reported dangers of distracted
OL,10,Fdriving and failing to wear seatbelts,
OL,11,Fthe numbers of people killed or
OL,12,Fseriously injured as a result of these
OL,13,Fbehaviours remain high.
OL,15,F"The technology AECOM is deploying
OL,16,Fmakes detection straightforward and is
OL,17,Fproviding valuable insight to the
OL,18,Fpolice and policy makers on the
OL,19,Fcurrent level of road user behaviour."
OL,26,@pD@YOUwD@AOU{D@fO]
