OL,6,FGeoff Collins, General Manager for
OL,7,FAcusensus UK said: "This is a
OL,8,Fsignificant milestone for UK road
OL,9,Fsafety. Our technology is now being
OL,10,Fused to directly deal with poor
OL,11,Fdriving behaviours, helping to break
OL,12,Fthose bad habits so making our roads
OL,13,Fsafer for everyone."
